quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  93,1,By the glorious morning light
  93,2,And by the night when it is still
  93,3,"Your Lord has not abandoned you, nor is He displeased"
  93,4,And indeed the future will be better for you than the present
  93,5,And soon your Lord will give you that with which you will be well pleased
  93,6,Did He not find you an orphan and give you shelter
  93,7,"And He found you wandering, and He gave you guidance"
  93,8,"And He found you in need, and made you independent"
  93,9,"Therefore, treat not the orphan with harshness"
  93,10,Nor refuse the petitioner
  93,11,"But the bounty of your Lord, proclaim"